'Tis the holiday decor season, and have we got a special decor treat for you! Robyn of @robyns_frenchnest joins us for a series of fabulous HOLIDAY DECOR TIPS you are simply going to love!⁠
⁠
Today she's talking DOUGH BOWLS, wonderful, versatile pieces for creating fabulous centerpieces. She makes it look so easy, right? Those twinkle lights are such a fun, creative addition!⁠
⁠
This DEEP WOODEN DOUGH BOWL with HANDLES is sure to amp up your centerpiece stylings all year long.⁠ Other style Dough Bowls also available.⁠
⁠

How did she do that? We've been asked before. And now. We have the answer! Danya of @avintageflarefarmhouse shares with us this awesome DIY DECOR HACK for how she styled our RETRO COWS WALL HANGING⁠ in her home.⁠

Wow! Who knew it could be so easy? Danya did! Thanks for sharing the how-to details with us. Love it!⁠
⁠
Danya's easy-peasy DIY hack is perfect for styling our RETRO COWS WALL HANGING as well as posters, scrolls, or decorative papers on your walls.⁠
